    "metadata": {
        "sysdescription": "Castor is a modest USFP transit system positioned between Helios, Kratos, and the Great Xim Gateway route to Memoras. Its importance comes from freight handling, customs oversight, and relief staging for Helios. It has some light manufacturing taking raw material from Kratos. It is the major customs point for traffic in and out of the Ximni Confederacy.",
